node.text:
I’m excited to announce I’ve teamed up with @bubblehouse_app to host a #drawthisinyourstyle challenge. There are physical prizes for this one including a few of the limited edition glitch girl pins that I have left, (swipe to see the prizes). The winners will be chosen at random so anyone who participates has a chance to win no matter what your skill level is. 

For anyone not familiar with @bubblehouse_app it’s a really cool app that allows you to post your art in more interactive ways including with before and after sliders (there’s an example of that on the last slide) and process sliders that show the progress of the whole piece. It’s a super cool app and I’d recommend it to anyone creative even if they’re not interested in this event. So-

Here’s how to enter! You can join on here or on the bubblehouse app or both! (Check my post on bubblehouse for the rules there)

1.) Create this in your style! You can draw it, 3D model it, photograph it etc. all styles are accepted!
 
2.) Upload your piece and include a video of it being used with a bubblehouse module! You have to have the bubblehouse app to do this, show a video of your piece with either the before/after slider or the process slider. (Your phone should have a built in screen recording setting for anyone who doesn’t know how to do this or there are screengrab apps you can use)

3.) Make sure to use the hashtag #lemonredraw2021 when you post.

4.) once you’re done comment ‘done’ along with which prize pack you want to win!

As I said before winners will be selected at random so all skill levels are invited to join. I’ll be creating a board on my bubblehouse page to share favorites as well. The deadline is September 30th. Some things to remember, if your profile is set to private I cannot see your entry even if you use the hashtag. Only entries posted to your page count I can’t accept entries via DM. Excited to see what you guys create!

#drawthisinyourstyle #dtiys #lemon #rainbow #sticker #art #artist #kawaii #anime #manga #cute #pinkhair

node.text:
I’m beyond pleased to announce that my shop is officially live! You can find it in the link in my bio! 

Being able to finally open this shop is my birthday gift to myself. It’s been so much work to get this all going but I’m really excited to have the shop finally open again. Last time it officially opened with a full stock like this was almost a year ago now. I’m thrilled to no longer have to feel overwhelmed about packaging every time I get orders now, honestly I could cry it’s such a big deal. The inventory would take up my whole house and I’d be walking through a sea of packaging and trying to get orders out fast while still managing making art, answering emails and patreon messages and going to meetings and so many other things, it was just too much. Being an artist is amazing but it’s also doing 20 different full time jobs all by yourself sometimes. Being able to get some help is such a necessity but oftentimes difficult to achieve so I can’t tell you how relieved I feel now to finally have my product in a fulfillment center and let the professionals do the shipping.
Anyway, I hope there are some things in there you guys like! And if you have requests for new products please let me know. And once again so sorry to everyone in the UK I promise I’m working as fast as I can to get all the VAT tax stuff worked out so I can ship to you I know it’s frustrating.

Happy shopping you guys and thanks so much for supporting my art!

Hello everyone! I have an official date and time for the shop launch!
The shop will be going live September 8th at 1PM pst (I’m excited, so I’m launching it on my birthday)

The shop drop will include another limited edition pin, the rainbow glitter headspace pin individually numbered on the back 1-200 (shown on the last slide). Some info:

-If you’re one of my patrons you’ll be receiving early access to the store so you can shop at your leisure, I’ve also launched a patreon secret store where you can now purchase past patreon rewards, be on the lookout for a patreon update that includes the password ❤️.

I think that’s all the info, I’ll set a countdown in my story as it gets closer to the date. If there’s any more questions you have let me know! Otherwise I’m very excited to finally be able to do this! It’s been a long time in the making

Headspace: This is one of my favorite pin designs so I thought it was high time I make a full illustration out of it.
Good news! I was safely able to get up to Seattle over the weekend and drop off all my product. Driving with all my product in one van was really intimidating, it was such a relief to get it dropped off. I have some more tweaks I’m doing to the store and some restocks that’s need to get done but i’m hoping sometime in August the store can open! Please let me know if there’s something you’d like to see in there like a specific print or keychain or something!
